- todo

- :skip_namespace (both DOM and SAX parsers)
 - options.skip_ns[256]
  - '\0' for no nothing
  - '*' for any
  - other string, compare start to pi->s against skip_ns

Values for the option would be nil or false to do nothing. That would be the default. If a string was provided then any namespace with that string on the element or attribute names would be stripped. If '*' or true was given then all namespaces would be stripped. 

